data.description: Refreshed and ready for you! Come see this charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home now on the market with renovations throughout as of March 2023! Enjoy this fully equipped kitchen that includes new granite counters, new stylish tile back splash, spacious and freshly painted cabinets, along modern black appliances. Discover a bright interior with new hard flooring throughout the main areas and a fireplace. A luxurious primary suite, complete with a completely renovated en-suite bathroom featuring a double stone topped vanity, beautiful tile surround shower, and a relaxing spa-like stand-alone tub. Upstairs bathroom has been renovated as well with new flooring and a brand-new stone-topped vanity. Step outside to your sparkling pool, and host the next gathering here! Don't miss this incredible opportunity! Please note glass shower door for the master bathroom is on back order and will be installed before close. This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
